{"tid":738053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被世界遺棄不可怕　薪俸稅有時還可怕！！","createTime":"2018-07-11T08:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T09:57:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0f262e0c6226e574a0f4b74b72867d66d06130","tid":738053,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2egz9lcgl7v72.cloudfront.net/CMS_images/NewsImage/2018-05-18-16-11-31eJ5Cp7Us.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2egz9lcgl7v72.cloudfront.net%2FCMS_images%2FNewsImage%2F2018-05-18-16-11-31eJ5Cp7Us.jpg&h=ed1b5edd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/725109/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/725109/page/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/zmo6vu3pizelre5/正在錄音2018-07-11%2015-35-11.wav?dl=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dropbox.com%2Fs%2Fzmo6vu3pizelre5%2F%E6%AD%A3%E5%9C%A8%E9%8C%84%E9%9F%B32018-07-11%252015-35-11.wav%3Fdl%3D0&d=JTRu4UmWOKpqXX3Vlp%2FPASwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c8ba79cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dropbox.com/s/zmo6vu3pizelre5/正在錄音2018-07-11%2015-35-11.wav?dl=0</a><br />\n<br />\n除非你是我的老母　待我　養活<br />\n無非你是我的政府　避稅　鐵了心<br />\n又要日曬　又要夜捱<br />\n讓你浪費　讓我瓦解<br />\n為你盛放　是廢青那媚態<br />\n<br />\n人過活要納稅　而遺產寬免嗎<br />\n填遺囑開替身　免再查<br />\n情愛就似納稅　長年不計代價<br />\n隨時不過換到　膠兩打<br />\n<br />\n被世界遺棄不可怕　薪俸稅有時還可怕 <br />\n被你建造百億高鐵　港珠澳在你手中火化<br />\n一收信　昂貴得可怕<br />\n寄錯吧　如何招架　強搶不好嗎<br />\n<br />\n誰盼望我納稅　存郵件於我家<br />\n長埋青色信封　已發芽<br />\n誰濫用我納稅　名堂千變萬化<br />\n持牌敲詐勒索　丟那媽<br />\n<br />\n被世界遺棄不可怕　薪俸稅有時還可怕 <br />\n被你褻玩那沙中綫　三跑也在你手中火化<br />\n一收信　昂貴得可怕<br />\n寄錯吧　如何招架　強搶不好嗎<br />\n<br />\n落雨了又有乜好怕　薪俸稅有時還可怕<br />\n地價貴沒降溫方法　搬遷你射上土星好嗎<br />\n枝火箭　隨你開天價<br />\n我當做　場場輸馬　神心得很嗎<br />\n<br />\n公帑裡　被徹底消化<br />\n我兩袖　全無牽掛　甚麼都不怕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big